Class NodeOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • NodeOperation
  • public class NodeOperation
extends java.lang.Object
    This library was designed to operate on a json structure that wants to simulate a filesystem. It is part of a larger project, but with small adaptations it can be used by anyone who wants to operate on json nodes. The library uses the Jackson json library; So if you want NodeOperation in the project you have to add the Jackson 2.12 library as well
    Version:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    bogojob@gmail.com
